{
  "stem": "26983.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to fill all kinds of formulas, exactly to write down every item, and many times.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything should be that even no food which could perish should be left, and everything should be in the best condition.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how to deliver the key.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Until the last detail-- how many kilos we can take with us and-- that was-- in the last detail thought of.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember, as a child, I was preparing for this in my way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was sent to a druggery to buy vitamins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Till today, I remember it was Vitamin B, D, C-- B and C vitamin pills.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the batteries, which were very useful for a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we got anti-typhoid injections.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vaccinations.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got all kinds of courses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How to behave and how to-- like Scouts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Months.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were the last ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Jewish community tried to teach us all kinds of jobs who may be useful for surviving.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And slowly, this kind of--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we could only take-- as far as I remember-- about 50 kilos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For a person.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we took on us the best clothes-- sometimes two shirts, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember very well the last day before we went to the so-called [GERMAN] or [GERMAN] from where they took us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The last time I took a bath, because two and a half years I didn't have a bath.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or I didn't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was the normal way before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember I put very carefully away my stamp collection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I put it on the roof somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You hid it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember we had some appointment with my best friends, who went one transport before me, which means only a couple of days before me.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
